title: [Old Ta'Faendryl, Market Road]
description: Wall surrounding an open plaza to the south run up against higher walls constructed of limestone blocks.  A heavy growth of vines and brambles creep along the wall in a dark, tangled mass of thorns and leaves.

Wall surrounding an open plaza to the south run up against higher walls constructed of limestone blocks.  The angular shape of the expertly cut blocks is barely visible through the heavy growth of vines and brambles growing along the full length of the wall.
